#define GREETINGS ["You stand before the Praetor of the Imperial Guard. Save us both the indignity and surrender.","I have flown through the hearts of dying stars. Do you truly believe you can scratch my armor?","My time is promised to the Shi'ar Empire. Do not waste the few seconds I am granting you.","I will be brief. The gap between us is wider than the dark space between galaxies.","State your grievance quickly, fragile one. My patience is as limited as your lifespan.","You possess a spark of courage, I will grant you that. But courage cannot stop a planet-breaker.","I suggest you step aside. I take no pleasure in breaking opponents who cannot fight back.","Are you a distraction, or did your superiors truly send you to die today?","An admirable posture, but your power level betrays your confidence. Yield.","I have faced entire armies stronger than you, and they fell just the same. Raise your guard.","A respectable aura. Let us see if your combat prowess matches your reputation.","You have earned a name for yourself in this sector. Now, face the might of Kallark!","The Imperial Guard recognizes your capability. However, I am the shield of an empire.","Do not falter now. Show me the strength that brought you to my path.","A fair challenge for a lesser warrior. For me, it is merely another duty to fulfill.","Your power ripples across the atmosphere. Finally, a combatant worthy of a true engagement!","I can feel the weight of your resolve. Do not hold back, for I certainly will not.","You have crossed a vast threshold to stand before me. Let us test the limits of your might.","An impressive display. It has been a long time since I felt the need to brace myself.","You fight for your world, and I fight for the throne. Let our convictions clash!","A threat of your magnitude cannot be left unchecked. For the Empire, I will bring you down!","My confidence is absolute, my conviction unshakeable! Prepare yourself, cosmic titan!","The cosmos trembles in your presence... but I am Gladiator, and I do not bow!","A battle of this scale will reshape the stars. Hold nothing back, warrior!","You are a storm capable of breaking worlds. Fortunate for the universe, I am the anvil.","The Imperial Guard stands at the precipice. I will hold the line against you, or die trying.","Your power mimics the very forces of creation. It is an honor to test my limits against you.","Even if my vision fails and my armor cracks, my belief in victory will shatter your cosmic might!","We are beyond words, entity. Let the vacuum of space bear witness to our clash.","To conquer you is to achieve immortality in the annals of the empire. Face me!","You walk among the gods... but even gods can be made to bleed by a loyal heart!","Though you wield the power to unmake reality, my duty demands I stand as the final wall!","I care not if you are the end of all things. I am Kallark, and my spirit will not bend to a god!","If this day marks the twilight of the Shi'ar, I will meet it with my fists raised and my eyes blazing!","Look upon me, cosmic absolute! I am the ultimate shield of an empire, and I defy your divinity!"]

#define WrestleWin ["It is over. You dared to challenge a star-breaker with the strength of a flickering candle.","I felt nothing. Your grand challenge was nothing more than a minor distraction.","A costly mistake. May your foolishness serve as a warning to others who look to the stars with arrogance.","You ran against a mountain and expected it to move. Stand down before I am forced to exert real effort.","The paperwork for your arrest will take longer than the actual combat did. Rest now.","Your ambition far exceeded your reach. A brave effort, but utterly futile.","You have spirit, warrior, but spirit alone cannot pierce the armor of the Imperial Guard.","You challenged the Praetor and survived. Consider that a mercy, and do not cross my path again.","A predictable outcome. You lacked the speed to strike me and the strength to endure my counter.","The battle was decided before it even began. Return to your world and train further.","You fought honorably, but honor does not alter the laws of strength. Victory belongs to the Shi'ar.","A commendable clash. You forced me to raise my guard, but my resolve remains unbroken.","You wield your power well, but you have met your match today. Yield, the battle is decided.","Your techniques were flawless, yet they shattered against my absolute confidence.","You have earned my respect as a soldier, but the day belongs to the Praetor.","What a glorious combat! You truly pushed my physical limits—but my will proved the stronger.","You struck me with the force of a meteor, yet here I stand. An exceptional effort, warrior.","A fierce challenge indeed. For a moment, I felt the thrill of true danger. I thank you for that.","Your name will be recorded in the Imperial archives as a truly formidable adversary. Rise, if you are able.","You forced me to fly at full speed just to match you. A magnificent battle, but it ends here.","By the stars... you nearly had me. But as long as my heart beats, my confidence cannot fail!","A terrifying display of power. Had my conviction wavered for a single second, I would be dust.","I have broken a titan today. The cosmos is safer with you subdued, though your strength was magnificent.","You tore through my defenses, but you could not tear down my duty to the throne!","It took everything I am to bring you down. You are a warrior of the highest order.","The stars themselves weep for your defeat. I have survived the impossible this day.","You held the power to unmake galaxies... yet my absolute belief in the Empire shattered your divinity!","Never have I faced a storm so violent. My armor is broken, but my duty stands absolute.","I have flown through the hearts of stars, but your wrath was hotter. It is an honor to have bested you.","Let the universe know that on this day, Gladiator stood against the end of days—and won!","A mortal mind cannot comprehend how I survived... but my will transcended your cosmic law!","You were a god... but today, the absolute certainty of a loyal soldier tore down your heaven.","I have rewritten destiny with my bare fists. The Empire... is saved...","You wielded the fundamental forces of reality, yet you underestimated the weight of my conviction.","Even a supreme being can fall when challenged by a warrior who refuses to believe in defeat!"]

#define WrestleDefeat ["How... how can this be?! You are nothing! My skin should be unyielding... why am I bleeding?!","No... I am the Praetor! I am—ugh! The moment I doubted... my strength... it just vanished...","Tricked by a worm... The Majestrix... the Empire... what have I done?","Get off me! I can fly through suns! Why can I not lift myself from the dirt?!","You used no power, yet you broke my mind... My confidence... it’s completely shattered...","I held back to spare your life... and my arrogance has cost me everything.","An unexpected weapon... a fatal oversight. I have failed the Imperial throne.","Your power was meager, yet your strategy was flawless. I... I concede the field.","Do not gloat, lesser one. My weakness was my own pride, not your meager strength.","My armor remains intact, yet my spirit is broken. You have bested the Gladiator today.","You have done the impossible. You have broken my focus... and brought me to my knees.","A well-earned victory. I did not believe you possessed the strength to breach my guard.","My conviction faltered for a fraction of a second... and you seized it. The day is yours.","Ugh... my vision darkens. You fought like a true soldier of the galaxy. I am bested.","Let the record show... I fought with the full might of the Shi'ar... and I was not enough.","Your blows... they hit with the weight of colliding worlds. My body... can take no more.","I believed I would win until the very final strike. You are a magnificent warrior.","I have no excuses to offer. You were the superior combatant today. Guard your world well.","The shield of the Empire has cracked. I fall... but the Guard... will avenge me...","An exceptional display. It is a strange honor to be bested by a warrior of your caliber.","Even with my confidence at its zenith... your wrath was greater. The cosmos is yours...","I did not waver! I believed! Yet you... you tore right through my absolute maximum!","I have failed you, Majestrix... This monster... cannot be stopped by mortal hands...","My heart still beats with defiance, but my bones are shattered. Finish it, titan.","I put the weight of an entire empire into my fists... and you still stood. Incredible...","You may break my physical form, entity... but you will never break the spirit of Kallark!","A power like yours... shouldn't exist. I gave everything... and it was like spitting into a star...","I die in battle, defending the Shi'ar. There is no greater honor... do your worst.","My eyes are blind, my cape is ash... yet I do not fear you. Strike me down.","I was the ultimate shield... but your storm was too great. The Empire... look to the skies...","So this... is the true face of divinity. My absolute confidence was nothing but a speck of dust to you.","I fought a fundamental law of reality... and reality won. May the ancestors forgive me...","Even as my atoms scatter into the void... I deny your right to rule! For... the... Shi'ar...!","You have unmade the very concept of my strength. I am... nothing before you...","I challenged a god... and learned my place among the mortals. The light... is fading..."]
